ElectricGuitarFractionFeature - Class in jsymbolic2.features
A feature exractor that finds the average number of notes that separate melodic peaks and troughs in any channel.
ElectricGuitarFractionFeature() - Constructor for class jsymbolic2.features.ElectricGuitarFractionFeature
Basic constructor that sets the definition and dependencies (and their offsets) of this feature.
ElectricInstrumentFractionFeature - Class in jsymbolic2.features
A feature exractor that finds the fraction of all Note Ons belonging to electric instrument patches (General MIDI patches 5, 6, 17, 19, 27 to 32 or 34 to 40).
ElectricInstrumentFractionFeature() - Constructor for class jsymbolic2.features.ElectricInstrumentFractionFeature
Basic constructor that sets the definition and dependencies (and their offsets) of this feature.
EmbellishmentFeature - Class in jsymbolic2.features
A feature extractor that extracts the fraction of notes that are surrounded on both sides by Note Ons on the same MIDI channel that have durations at least three times as long as the central note.
EmbellishmentFeature() - Constructor for class jsymbolic2.features.EmbellishmentFeature
Basic constructor that sets the definition and dependencies (and their offsets) of this feature.
